{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2c8cd284b","title":"广西省容县、宜山两专区最近约有一万一千名农业社社员闹退社","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ea50cad096","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":11,"articleId":"f2c8cd284b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"40e3e0f35a","name":"李益芳"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bdb005e273","type":"title","text":"广西省容县、宜山两专区最近约有一万一千名农业社社员闹退社","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"087e5c14e7","type":"authors","text":"李益芳","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"1a75fbeb91","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南宁11日讯　广西省容县、宜山两专区部分农业社社员闹退社现象最近又有发展。据十个县的不完全统计，有一万一千多户社员闹退社。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"037f1cf9f8","type":"paragraph","text":"闹退社的原因有二：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"4f854d98ff","type":"paragraph","text":"一、富裕农户不愿参加社。如苍梧县思委农业社闹退社的七十四户中，富农和富裕农户就有三十四户。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"70819d71a2","type":"paragraph","text":"二、部分社员目前生活困难，失掉生产信心。据贵县十六个农业社五千八百多户社员收入的调查，去年秋收分配平均每人分得稻谷二十至一百斤的就有三千二百多户，这些户社员现在已经没有口粮，他们说：没有粮食怎样能出工。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"},{"id":"c793b07f2c","type":"paragraph","text":"1957年3月11日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b"}],"page":{"id":"eea234fef8","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f2c8cd284b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}